Pierre Palau https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pierre_Palau 0 Pierre Palau (13 August 1883 – 3 December 1966), often known simply as Palau, was a French actor. Palau was born Pierre Palau del Vitri in Pairs and died at age 83 in Meudon, Hauts-de-Seine, France.
